snippet.title: Oh No! I Died and Woke Up a Greek God!
snippet.description:
Oh No! You died and were reborn as a god on Mount Olympus! Your goal is to find a way back to Earth! The problem? Gods keep falling in love with you! Go on dates, party through the night, and find out what’s happening on this crazy mountain!
Now on Steam!
